data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this charming single-family home featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a one-car garage, and a refreshing pool. Centrally located in the heart of Pembroke Pines, this residence offers a lifestyle of ease and relaxation. Your dream home awaits!  2023: New Oven and Microwave  2022: New Roof, Exterior Paint and New Dishwasher  2021: New Pool Pump  2019: New AC and Pool Liner
